Context Menu for Google Translate™
Chrome Extension
Adds a right-click menu item that makes it easy to translate selected text in Google Translate™.

Copyright 2011 Brandon Thomson
License: BSD

This extension is available on the Chrome web store at:
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/kigmfpmcomhecmajcfiianbhjgcenado

I'll accept pull requests for bugfixes and reasonable features.

If you fork this extension and publish your own copy in the Chrome web store,
please use a different 128x128 icon or at least alter it in a major way. This
helps prevent user confusion in the search results.
